We generally encourage having the *“learning from deployment”* idea, and projects should focus on talent sourcing (GitHub, X, arXiv, linkedin, etc.), personalized outreach sequencing, technical assessment generation, interview scheduling, reference checking, or full-cycle candidate relationship management.
